    <sect3 role="package">
      <title>Introduction to Smartypants Module</title>

      <para>
        <application>Smartypants</application> translates plain ASCII
        punctuation characters into <quote>smart</quote> typographic
        punctuation HTML entities.
      </para>

      &lfs113_checked;

